"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-arts-entertainment-music-news-celine-dion-olympics-paris-song-b2586894.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Singer hit pause on performing in 2022 as she learnt to live with stiff person syndrome  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Celine Dionhas said she is \\\"so full of joy\\\" after making asurprise return to the stage for the first timesince she was diagnosed with stiff person syndrome in 2022.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"My Heart Will Go On\\\" singerleft fans teary eyed when she performed fromtheEiffel Towerduring the Olympics opening ceremony in Paris on Friday night (26 July), with a moving rendition ofEdith Piaf's \\\"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour\\\".\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.112488824583183e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was her first performance since 2022, when she was diagnosed with the rare, incurable disorder, which causes rigidity in the torso and limbs, as well as severe muscle spasms.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was subsequently forced to cancel her world tour as she focused on learning to live with the condition.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion said in a social media post that she is \\\"so full of joy to be back in one my favourite cities\\\".\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of all, I am so happy to be celebrating these amazing athletes, with all their stories of sacrifice and determination, pain and perseverance,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All of you have been so focused on your dream, and whether or not you take home a medal, I hope that being here means that it has come true for you!\\\"\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 56-year-old continued: \\\"You should all be so proud, we know how hard you have worked to be the best of the best.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay focused, keep going, my heart is with you!\\\"\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During her performance, Dion wore a glistening, bead-covered dress as the rain dramatically poured down onto the grand piano being played behind her.\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SPS is an autoimmune and neurological disorder that causes rigidity in the torso and limbs.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Proton_Synchrotron\", \"score\": 0.9148623989122305, \"rank\": 0.08308800074576773, \"text\": \"SPS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Proton_Synchrotron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_Proton_Synchrotron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Symptoms include stiffening in the torso and limbs, along with muscle spasms.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion has previously said that when her condition is at its worst, it feels like someone is pushing on her larynx and pharynx when she tries to sing.\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy unlimited access to 100 million ad-free songs and podcasts with Amazon Music  Sign up now for a 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Terms apply.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you sign up to this service we will earn commission.This revenue helps to fund journalism across The Independent.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy unlimited access to 100 million ad-free songs and podcasts with Amazon Music  Sign up now for a 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Terms apply.\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you sign up to this service we will earn commission.This revenue helps to fund journalism across The Independent.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Periods of muscle spasming can be triggered differently between people, but environmental stimuli like loud noises, stress, touch, cold temperatures or performing certain exercises, could trigger spasms in some people.\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, Dion explained that herspasms can occur unexpectedly, like when she's cooking at home or singing.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It gets into a spasm,\\\" she told NBC's Hoda Kotb in a filmed interview.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3062, \"end\": 3065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999616093199, \"rank\": 3.838071742194513e-08, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 3068, \"end\": 3077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hoda Kotb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hoda_Kotb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It can also be in the abdominal, it can also be in my spine, in my ribs.\\\"\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I point my feet, they will stay [in the same position], or if I cook, because I love to cook, my hands will get in a position where you cannot unlock them.\\\"\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion revealed her spasms were so severe that she previously had a broken a rib.\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans were overjoyed to see Dion perform again in Paris, with one viewer writing on X/Twitter: \\\"Celine Dion with one of the most beautiful performances you will ever see.\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3469, \"end\": 3474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.112488824583183e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With all that she has been thru she has me in tears.\\\"\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[sic]  Another added that her performance was \\\"totally worth the wait.\\\"\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow The Independent's Paris 2024 Olympics live blog here for real-time updates.\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged 